# Ultimate Genius Chat: a fresh start

The purpose of _Ultimate Genius Chat_ is to build *the* best thing that we can build, with the latest and greatest tools and libraries.<br>
Clean code. Function-ize. 
Test, test, test. 
Read the documentation.

There. Now that we've gotten that out of the way,

# Major Changes:
- Websockets. 
- Node.js.
- End-to-end encryption
- Mobile-first UI mindset
- Flexbox
- SCSS
and more...

